OL,7,FThe terrorism definition should not be
OL,8,Fchanged in the wake of the Southport
OL,9,Fmurders but a new offence to address
OL,10,Fthe gap for lone individuals planning
OL,11,Fmass killings should be considered,
OL,12,Fthe UK's terror watchdog has said.
OL,14,FJonathan Hall KC said the legal
OL,15,Fdefinition is "already wide" and
OL,16,Fexpanding the threshold would
OL,17,F"increase the possibility of
OL,18,Finaccurate use and, in theory, abuse".
