OL,7,FThe warning comes after Prime Minister
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer questioned whether
OL,9,Fterror laws should change in the face
OL,10,Fof the "new threat" posed by violent
OL,11,Floners such as the Southport murderer.
OL,13,FMr Hall's review commissioned by the
OL,14,FHome Secretary in January to examine
OL,15,Fterror legislation "in light of modern
OL,16,Fthreats we face" also warns that
OL,17,Fextending terror liability could
OL,18,Fresult in "unacceptable restrictions
OL,19,Fon freedom of expression".
