OL,14,Fminimum of 52 years for the murders of
OL,15,Fthree girls and attempted murders of
OL,16,Feight other children, who cannot be
OL,17,Fnamed for legal reasons, class
OL,18,Finstructor Leanne Lucas and
OL,19,Fbusinessman John Hayes at a Taylor
OL,20,FSwift-themed dance class in July last
OL,21,Fyear.
