OL,7,FDespite contact with state agencies
OL,8,Fsuch as Prevent, aimed at countering
OL,9,Fterrorism, authorities failed to stop
OL,10,Fthe attack which claimed the lives of
OL,11,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,12,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,13,Fseven.
OL,15,FRudakubana's acts of extreme violence
OL,16,Fwere not considered terrorism under
OL,17,Fexisting laws because there was no
OL,18,Fevidence of his purpose being to
OL,19,Fadvance an ideological cause as set
OL,20,Fout in the terror definition.
