OL,7,FBut Mr Hall said: "Such is the
OL,8,Ffunctional importance of the terrorism
OL,9,Fdefinition, that redefinition would
OL,10,Falter the landscape.
OL,12,F"It would risk major false positives `
OL,13,Fthe prosecution of people who by no
OL,14,Fstretch of the imagination are
OL,15,Fterrorists ` and extend terrorism
OL,16,Fliability into novel terrain.
OL,18,F"People swapping violent war footage
OL,19,Fwould be at risk of encouraging
OL,20,Fterrorism, resulting in unacceptable
OL,21,Frestrictions on freedom of expression."
