OL,7,FInstead, the watchdog recommended
OL,8,Fcreating an offence to prevent mass
OL,9,Fcasualty attacks before they happen,
OL,10,Fsimilar to terrorism offences applying
OL,11,Fto an offender preparing for an attack.
