OL,7,FElsewhere Mr Hall warned that
OL,8,Fdisinformation in the aftermath of the
OL,9,FSouthport killings and allegations of
OL,10,Fa "cover-up" risked far more prejudice
OL,11,Fto any trial than undisputed facts
OL,12,Fabout the attacker.
OL,14,F"In the digital era, if the police do
OL,15,Fnot take the lead in providing clear,
OL,16,Faccurate and sober details about an
OL,17,Fattack like Southport, others will,"
