OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,Fhorrific attack in Southport last July
OL,9,Fcost the lives of three young girls
OL,10,Fand left others with lifelong physical
OL,11,Fand emotional damage. We have pledged
OL,12,Fto not only get justice for the
OL,13,Fvictims and their families, but also
OL,14,Fbring about the changes needed to
OL,15,Fprevent such a horror from happening
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,F"Today's report is an important step
OL,19,Fin that search for answers, and to
OL,20,Ftackle horrific acts driven by a
OL,21,Ffixation on extreme violence.
OL,26,@oD@aOUzD@AOU
