OL,7,F"As the Prime Minister said at the
OL,8,Ftime, if the law needs to change, we
OL,9,Fwill change it and, on the back of
OL,10,Ftoday's report, we will fix the
OL,11,Flegislation to close the gaps
OL,12,Fidentified.
OL,14,F"We also agree that we must look at
OL,15,Fhow social media is putting long-
OL,16,Festablished principles around how we
OL,17,Fcommunicate after an attack like this
OL,18,Funder strain.
